	   <tr><td colspan=2>Right on!!!<br>People seem to have lost the role-playing aspect and are only around for hack 'n slash.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Play a race/class you enjoy.  Even if your stats blow for the class your playing I bet over time you will level higher with a character you enjoy playing than then with one that has ideal stats. <br><br>If you are not particular about race think about it this way:  With a high STR but low WIS you do more damage but you spells fizzle more, and with a higher WIS . . . you get the idea.  If you want to solo more play a race with higher STR.  If you want to group more play a race with higher WIS. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
