	   <tr><td colspan=2>I started my lvl 1 HFL cleric with Jboot (multiquest), 160WIS and super fast 1HB (backjack) to push his 1HB skill.<br><br>Out of all races, only DWF and HFL CLR can melee for higher lvls.&nbsp;&nbsp;But ultimately, when CLR reaches lvl 50, their buff/heal 99% of the time in grp.<br><br>I think DWF CLR got the best stats to start off but HFL is on par with the hide/sneak skills (no invis spell for CLR other than invis vs undead).  Give these 2 skills, plus I can push my CLR's stats using items and jewelries, I'll go for a HFL CLR. <br><br>Another big adventage for HFL CLR is tat they lvl slightly faster than other classes, which is better for the first 20 lvl of soloing (with Jboot, I just flee to zone when I lost the fight).<br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
